title: VAN HALEN Women And Children First. (PBTHAL Vinyl) FLAC
description:
Turntable: VPI Scoutmaster
Tonearm: Trans-Fi Terminator Air Bearing Linear Tracking
Cartridge: Audio-Technica AT33PTG
Phono Preamp: Pro-Ject TubeBox
Soundcard: E-MU 1212

Recorded in full 192khz resolution and then resampled to 44/24 for manual click repair.  Dithered to standard redbook 16bit/44khz.  IzotopeRX Advanced used for all resampling/dithering

This and Fair Warning are my favorite VH albums... pour the Jack Daniels!

Ripped by PBTHAL. THANK YOU Patrick! Your rig continues to sound fantastic....
